{"word":"G1538 - ἕκαστος - hékastos - hek'-as-tos - Any","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἕκαστος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hékastos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hek'-as-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Any</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அந்தந்த, ஒவ்வொரு, ஒவ்வொன்று - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"each, every"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>As if a superlative of <b>&#x03B5;&#x0314;&#x0301;&#x03BA;&#x03B1;&#x03C2;</b> <b>hekas</b> (<i>afar</i>); <i>each</i> or <i>every:</i> - any, both, each (one), every (man, one, woman), particularly.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}